{
  "book": "2nephi",
  "bookName": "2 Nephi",
  "chapter": 25,
  "voice": {
    "provider": "elevenlabs",
    "voice_id": "ddDFRErfhdc2asyySOG5",
    "model_id": "eleven_multilingual_v2",
    "settings": {
      "stability": 0.5,
      "similarity_boost": 0.75,
      "style": 0.35,
      "use_speaker_boost": true
    },
    "name": "samuel"
  },
  "pauses": {
    "line_ms": 180,
    "verse_ms": 500
  },
  "duration": 639.251,
  "lines": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 2.415,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Now I, Nephi, do speak somewhat",
      "verse": "25:1",
      "lineIndex": 1
    },
    {
      "start": 2.595,
      "end": 5.242,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "concerning the words which I have written,",
      "verse": "25:1",
      "lineIndex": 2
    },
    {
      "start": 5.422,
      "end": 8.162,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which have been spoken by the mouth of Isaiah.",
      "verse": "25:1",
      "lineIndex": 3
    },
    {
      "start": 8.342,
      "end": 11.128,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "For behold, Isaiah spake many things",
      "verse": "25:1",
      "lineIndex": 4
    },
    {
      "start": 11.308,
      "end": 14.605,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which were hard for many of my people to understand;",
      "verse": "25:1",
      "lineIndex": 5
    },
    {
      "start": 14.785,
      "end": 19.011,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for they know not concerning the manner of prophesying among the Jews.",
      "verse": "25:1",
      "lineIndex": 6
    },
    {
      "start": 19.691,
      "end": 22.942,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "For I, Nephi, have not taught them many things",
      "verse": "25:2",
      "lineIndex": 7
    },
    {
      "start": 23.122,
      "end": 25.444,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "concerning the manner of the Jews;",
      "verse": "25:2",
      "lineIndex": 8
    },
    {
      "start": 25.624,
      "end": 28.318,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for their works were works of darkness,",
      "verse": "25:2",
      "lineIndex": 9
    },
    {
      "start": 28.498,
      "end": 31.609,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and their doings were doings of abominations.",
      "verse": "25:2",
      "lineIndex": 10
    },
    {
      "start": 32.289,
      "end": 34.425,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore, I write unto my people,",
      "verse": "25:3",
      "lineIndex": 12
    },
    {
      "start": 34.605,
      "end": 37.252,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "unto all those that shall receive hereafter",
      "verse": "25:3",
      "lineIndex": 13
    },
    {
      "start": 37.432,
      "end": 39.15,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "these things which I write,",
      "verse": "25:3",
      "lineIndex": 14
    },
    {
      "start": 39.33,
      "end": 42.209,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that they may know the judgments of God,",
      "verse": "25:3",
      "lineIndex": 15
    },
    {
      "start": 42.389,
      "end": 44.804,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that they come upon all nations,",
      "verse": "25:3",
      "lineIndex": 16
    },
    {
      "start": 44.984,
      "end": 47.445,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "according to the word which he hath spoken.",
      "verse": "25:3",
      "lineIndex": 17
    },
    {
      "start": 48.125,
      "end": 50.215,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore, hearken, O my people,",
      "verse": "25:4",
      "lineIndex": 18
    },
    {
      "start": 50.395,
      "end": 52.949,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which are of the house of Israel,",
      "verse": "25:4",
      "lineIndex": 19
    },
    {
      "start": 53.129,
      "end": 55.219,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and give ear unto my words;",
      "verse": "25:4",
      "lineIndex": 20
    },
    {
      "start": 55.399,
      "end": 58.882,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for because the words of Isaiah are not plain unto you,",
      "verse": "25:4",
      "lineIndex": 21
    },
    {
      "start": 59.062,
      "end": 63.845,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "nevertheless they are plain unto all those that are filled with the spirit of prophecy.",
      "verse": "25:4",
      "lineIndex": 22
    },
    {
      "start": 64.025,
      "end": 66.068,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "But I give unto you a prophecy,",
      "verse": "25:4",
      "lineIndex": 23
    },
    {
      "start": 66.248,
      "end": 68.616,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "according to the spirit which is in me;",
      "verse": "25:4",
      "lineIndex": 24
    },
    {
      "start": 68.796,
      "end": 74.137,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherefore I shall prophesy according to the plainness which hath been with me",
      "verse": "25:4",
      "lineIndex": 25
    },
    {
      "start": 74.317,
      "end": 78.079,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "from the time that I came out from Jerusalem with my father;",
      "verse": "25:4",
      "lineIndex": 26
    },
    {
      "start": 78.259,
      "end": 81.788,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for behold, my soul delighteth in plainness unto my people,",
      "verse": "25:4",
      "lineIndex": 27
    },
    {
      "start": 81.968,
      "end": 83.454,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that they may learn.",
      "verse": "25:4",
      "lineIndex": 28
    },
    {
      "start": 84.134,
      "end": 87.06,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Yea, and my soul delighteth in the words of Isaiah,",
      "verse": "25:5",
      "lineIndex": 29
    },
    {
      "start": 87.24,
      "end": 89.469,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for I came out from Jerusalem,",
      "verse": "25:5",
      "lineIndex": 30
    },
    {
      "start": 89.649,
      "end": 92.9,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and mine eyes hath beheld the things of the Jews,",
      "verse": "25:5",
      "lineIndex": 31
    },
    {
      "start": 93.08,
      "end": 97.77,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I know that the Jews do understand the things of the prophets,",
      "verse": "25:5",
      "lineIndex": 32
    },
    {
      "start": 97.95,
      "end": 104.127,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and there is none other people that understand the things which were spoken unto the Jews",
      "verse": "25:5",
      "lineIndex": 33
    },
    {
      "start": 104.307,
      "end": 105.793,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "like unto them,",
      "verse": "25:5",
      "lineIndex": 34
    },
    {
      "start": 105.973,
      "end": 110.524,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "save it be that they are taught after the manner of the things of the Jews.",
      "verse": "25:5",
      "lineIndex": 35
    },
    {
      "start": 111.204,
      "end": 115.941,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "But behold, I, Nephi, have not taught my children after the manner of the Jews;",
      "verse": "25:6",
      "lineIndex": 36
    },
    {
      "start": 116.121,
      "end": 119.65,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "but behold, I, of myself, have dwelt at Jerusalem,",
      "verse": "25:6",
      "lineIndex": 37
    },
    {
      "start": 119.83,
      "end": 123.592,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherefore I know concerning the regions round about;",
      "verse": "25:6",
      "lineIndex": 38
    },
    {
      "start": 123.772,
      "end": 128.602,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I have made mention unto my children concerning the judgments of God,",
      "verse": "25:6",
      "lineIndex": 39
    },
    {
      "start": 128.782,
      "end": 133.054,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which hath come to pass among the Jews, unto my children,",
      "verse": "25:6",
      "lineIndex": 40
    },
    {
      "start": 133.234,
      "end": 136.16,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "according to all that which Isaiah hath spoken,",
      "verse": "25:6",
      "lineIndex": 41
    },
    {
      "start": 136.34,
      "end": 137.919,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I do not write them.",
      "verse": "25:6",
      "lineIndex": 42
    },
    {
      "start": 138.599,
      "end": 141.478,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "But behold, I proceed with mine own prophecy,",
      "verse": "25:7",
      "lineIndex": 43
    },
    {
      "start": 141.658,
      "end": 143.33,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "according to my plainness;",
      "verse": "25:7",
      "lineIndex": 44
    },
    {
      "start": 143.51,
      "end": 146.157,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "in the which I know that no man can err;",
      "verse": "25:7",
      "lineIndex": 45
    },
    {
      "start": 146.337,
      "end": 150.842,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "nevertheless, in the days that the prophecies of Isaiah shall be fulfilled",
      "verse": "25:7",
      "lineIndex": 46
    },
    {
      "start": 151.022,
      "end": 153.39,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "men shall know of a surety,",
      "verse": "25:7",
      "lineIndex": 47
    },
    {
      "start": 153.57,
      "end": 155.938,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "at the times when they shall come to pass.",
      "verse": "25:7",
      "lineIndex": 48
    },
    {
      "start": 156.618,
      "end": 160.194,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore, they are of worth unto the children of men,",
      "verse": "25:8",
      "lineIndex": 50
    },
    {
      "start": 160.374,
      "end": 162.835,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and he that supposeth that they are not,",
      "verse": "25:8",
      "lineIndex": 51
    },
    {
      "start": 163.015,
      "end": 165.383,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "unto them will I speak particularly,",
      "verse": "25:8",
      "lineIndex": 52
    },
    {
      "start": 165.563,
      "end": 168.674,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and confine the words unto mine own people;",
      "verse": "25:8",
      "lineIndex": 53
    },
    {
      "start": 168.854,
      "end": 173.591,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for I know that they shall be of great worth unto them in the last days;",
      "verse": "25:8",
      "lineIndex": 54
    },
    {
      "start": 173.771,
      "end": 176.372,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for in that day shall they understand them;",
      "verse": "25:8",
      "lineIndex": 55
    },
    {
      "start": 176.552,
      "end": 179.71,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherefore, for their good have I written them.",
      "verse": "25:8",
      "lineIndex": 56
    },
    {
      "start": 180.39,
      "end": 182.619,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And as one generation hath been destroyed",
      "verse": "25:9",
      "lineIndex": 57
    },
    {
      "start": 182.799,
      "end": 185.214,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "among the Jews because of iniquity,",
      "verse": "25:9",
      "lineIndex": 58
    },
    {
      "start": 185.394,
      "end": 187.902,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "even so have they been destroyed",
      "verse": "25:9",
      "lineIndex": 59
    },
    {
      "start": 188.082,
      "end": 191.844,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "from generation to generation according to their iniquities;",
      "verse": "25:9",
      "lineIndex": 60
    },
    {
      "start": 192.024,
      "end": 194.625,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and never hath any of them been destroyed",
      "verse": "25:9",
      "lineIndex": 61
    },
    {
      "start": 194.805,
      "end": 198.149,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "save it were foretold them by the prophets of the Lord.",
      "verse": "25:9",
      "lineIndex": 62
    },
    {
      "start": 198.829,
      "end": 203.519,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore, it hath been told them concerning the destruction which should come upon them,",
      "verse": "25:10",
      "lineIndex": 63
    },
    {
      "start": 203.699,
      "end": 206.3,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "immediately after my father left Jerusalem;",
      "verse": "25:10",
      "lineIndex": 64
    },
    {
      "start": 206.48,
      "end": 208.802,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "nevertheless, they hardened their hearts;",
      "verse": "25:10",
      "lineIndex": 65
    },
    {
      "start": 208.982,
      "end": 212.233,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and according to my prophecy they have been destroyed,",
      "verse": "25:10",
      "lineIndex": 66
    },
    {
      "start": 212.413,
      "end": 216.082,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "save it be those which are carried away captive into Babylon.",
      "verse": "25:10",
      "lineIndex": 67
    },
    {
      "start": 216.762,
      "end": 220.059,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And now this I speak because of the spirit which is in me.",
      "verse": "25:11",
      "lineIndex": 68
    },
    {
      "start": 220.239,
      "end": 222.793,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And notwithstanding they have been carried away",
      "verse": "25:11",
      "lineIndex": 69
    },
    {
      "start": 222.973,
      "end": 224.691,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "they shall return again,",
      "verse": "25:11",
      "lineIndex": 70
    },
    {
      "start": 224.871,
      "end": 227.1,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and possess the land of Jerusalem;",
      "verse": "25:11",
      "lineIndex": 71
    },
    {
      "start": 227.28,
      "end": 232.806,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherefore, they shall be restored again to the land of their inheritance.",
      "verse": "25:11",
      "lineIndex": 72
    },
    {
      "start": 233.486,
      "end": 237.805,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "But, behold, they shall have wars, and rumors of wars;",
      "verse": "25:12",
      "lineIndex": 73
    },
    {
      "start": 237.985,
      "end": 241.747,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and when the day cometh that the Only Begotten of the Father,",
      "verse": "25:12",
      "lineIndex": 74
    },
    {
      "start": 241.927,
      "end": 245.178,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yea, even the Father of heaven and of earth,",
      "verse": "25:12",
      "lineIndex": 75
    },
    {
      "start": 245.358,
      "end": 248.609,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "shall manifest himself unto them in the flesh,",
      "verse": "25:12",
      "lineIndex": 76
    },
    {
      "start": 248.789,
      "end": 251.157,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "behold, they will reject him,",
      "verse": "25:12",
      "lineIndex": 77
    },
    {
      "start": 251.337,
      "end": 253.334,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "because of their iniquities,",
      "verse": "25:12",
      "lineIndex": 78
    },
    {
      "start": 253.514,
      "end": 255.464,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the hardness of their hearts,",
      "verse": "25:12",
      "lineIndex": 79
    },
    {
      "start": 255.644,
      "end": 257.873,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the stiffness of their necks.",
      "verse": "25:12",
      "lineIndex": 80
    },
    {
      "start": 258.553,
      "end": 260.596,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Behold, they will crucify him;",
      "verse": "25:13",
      "lineIndex": 81
    },
    {
      "start": 260.776,
      "end": 264.213,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and after he is laid in a sepulchre for the space of three days",
      "verse": "25:13",
      "lineIndex": 82
    },
    {
      "start": 264.393,
      "end": 267.783,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "he shall rise from the dead, with healing in his wings;",
      "verse": "25:13",
      "lineIndex": 83
    },
    {
      "start": 267.963,
      "end": 272.7,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and all those who shall believe on his name shall be saved in the kingdom of God.",
      "verse": "25:13",
      "lineIndex": 84
    },
    {
      "start": 272.88,
      "end": 276.27,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore, my soul delighteth to prophesy concerning him,",
      "verse": "25:13",
      "lineIndex": 85
    },
    {
      "start": 276.45,
      "end": 278.029,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for I have seen his day,",
      "verse": "25:13",
      "lineIndex": 86
    },
    {
      "start": 278.209,
      "end": 280.81,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and my heart doth magnify his holy name.",
      "verse": "25:13",
      "lineIndex": 87
    },
    {
      "start": 281.49,
      "end": 286.366,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And behold it shall come to pass that after the Messiah hath risen from the dead,",
      "verse": "25:14",
      "lineIndex": 88
    },
    {
      "start": 286.546,
      "end": 289.332,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and hath manifested himself unto his people,",
      "verse": "25:14",
      "lineIndex": 89
    },
    {
      "start": 289.512,
      "end": 292.206,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "unto as many as will believe on his name,",
      "verse": "25:14",
      "lineIndex": 90
    },
    {
      "start": 292.386,
      "end": 294.894,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "behold, Jerusalem shall be destroyed again;",
      "verse": "25:14",
      "lineIndex": 91
    },
    {
      "start": 295.074,
      "end": 299.811,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for wo unto them that fight against God and the people of his church.",
      "verse": "25:14",
      "lineIndex": 92
    },
    {
      "start": 300.491,
      "end": 304.067,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore, the Jews shall be scattered among all nations;",
      "verse": "25:15",
      "lineIndex": 93
    },
    {
      "start": 304.247,
      "end": 306.848,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yea, and also Babylon shall be destroyed;",
      "verse": "25:15",
      "lineIndex": 94
    },
    {
      "start": 307.028,
      "end": 310.325,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherefore, the Jews shall be scattered by other nations.",
      "verse": "25:15",
      "lineIndex": 95
    },
    {
      "start": 311.005,
      "end": 313.048,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And after they have been scattered,",
      "verse": "25:16",
      "lineIndex": 97
    },
    {
      "start": 313.228,
      "end": 315.782,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the Lord God hath scourged them",
      "verse": "25:16",
      "lineIndex": 98
    },
    {
      "start": 315.962,
      "end": 319.538,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "by other nations for the space of many generations,",
      "verse": "25:16",
      "lineIndex": 99
    },
    {
      "start": 319.718,
      "end": 322.829,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yea, even down from generation to generation",
      "verse": "25:16",
      "lineIndex": 100
    },
    {
      "start": 323.009,
      "end": 327.281,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "until they shall be persuaded to believe in Christ, the Son of God,",
      "verse": "25:16",
      "lineIndex": 101
    },
    {
      "start": 327.461,
      "end": 330.619,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the atonement, which is infinite for all mankind\u2014",
      "verse": "25:16",
      "lineIndex": 102
    },
    {
      "start": 330.799,
      "end": 334.143,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and when that day shall come that they shall believe in Christ,",
      "verse": "25:16",
      "lineIndex": 103
    },
    {
      "start": 334.323,
      "end": 336.599,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and worship the Father in his name,",
      "verse": "25:16",
      "lineIndex": 104
    },
    {
      "start": 336.779,
      "end": 339.147,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "with pure hearts and clean hands,",
      "verse": "25:16",
      "lineIndex": 105
    },
    {
      "start": 339.327,
      "end": 342.624,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and look not forward any more for another Messiah,",
      "verse": "25:16",
      "lineIndex": 106
    },
    {
      "start": 342.804,
      "end": 344.987,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "then, at that time, the day will come",
      "verse": "25:16",
      "lineIndex": 107
    },
    {
      "start": 345.167,
      "end": 349.857,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that it must needs be expedient that they should believe these things.",
      "verse": "25:16",
      "lineIndex": 108
    },
    {
      "start": 350.537,
      "end": 353.834,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And the Lord will set his hand again the second time",
      "verse": "25:17",
      "lineIndex": 109
    },
    {
      "start": 354.014,
      "end": 357.497,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "to restore his people from their lost and fallen state.",
      "verse": "25:17",
      "lineIndex": 110
    },
    {
      "start": 357.677,
      "end": 362.042,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore, he will proceed to do a marvelous work and a wonder",
      "verse": "25:17",
      "lineIndex": 111
    },
    {
      "start": 362.222,
      "end": 363.94,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "among the children of men.",
      "verse": "25:17",
      "lineIndex": 112
    },
    {
      "start": 364.62,
      "end": 367.871,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore, he shall bring forth his words unto them,",
      "verse": "25:18",
      "lineIndex": 113
    },
    {
      "start": 368.051,
      "end": 371.255,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which words shall judge them at the last day,",
      "verse": "25:18",
      "lineIndex": 114
    },
    {
      "start": 371.435,
      "end": 373.432,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for they shall be given them",
      "verse": "25:18",
      "lineIndex": 115
    },
    {
      "start": 373.612,
      "end": 377.002,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for the purpose of convincing them of the true Messiah,",
      "verse": "25:18",
      "lineIndex": 116
    },
    {
      "start": 377.182,
      "end": 379.086,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "who was rejected by them;",
      "verse": "25:18",
      "lineIndex": 117
    },
    {
      "start": 379.266,
      "end": 381.542,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and unto the convincing of them",
      "verse": "25:18",
      "lineIndex": 118
    },
    {
      "start": 381.722,
      "end": 385.716,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that they need not look forward any more for a Messiah to come,",
      "verse": "25:18",
      "lineIndex": 119
    },
    {
      "start": 385.896,
      "end": 388.032,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for there should not any come,",
      "verse": "25:18",
      "lineIndex": 120
    },
    {
      "start": 388.212,
      "end": 390.488,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "save it should be a false Messiah",
      "verse": "25:18",
      "lineIndex": 121
    },
    {
      "start": 390.668,
      "end": 393.176,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which should deceive the people;",
      "verse": "25:18",
      "lineIndex": 122
    },
    {
      "start": 393.356,
      "end": 397.118,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for there is save one Messiah spoken of by the prophets,",
      "verse": "25:18",
      "lineIndex": 123
    },
    {
      "start": 397.298,
      "end": 400.735,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and that Messiah is he who should be rejected of the Jews.",
      "verse": "25:18",
      "lineIndex": 124
    },
    {
      "start": 401.415,
      "end": 404.062,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "For according to the words of the prophets,",
      "verse": "25:19",
      "lineIndex": 125
    },
    {
      "start": 404.242,
      "end": 406.61,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "the Messiah cometh in six hundred years",
      "verse": "25:19",
      "lineIndex": 126
    },
    {
      "start": 406.79,
      "end": 409.994,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "from the time that my father left Jerusalem;",
      "verse": "25:19",
      "lineIndex": 127
    },
    {
      "start": 410.174,
      "end": 412.682,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and according to the words of the prophets,",
      "verse": "25:19",
      "lineIndex": 128
    },
    {
      "start": 412.862,
      "end": 415.23,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also the word of the angel of God,",
      "verse": "25:19",
      "lineIndex": 129
    },
    {
      "start": 415.41,
      "end": 418.336,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "his name shall be Jesus Christ, the Son of God.",
      "verse": "25:19",
      "lineIndex": 130
    },
    {
      "start": 419.016,
      "end": 420.502,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And now, my brethren,",
      "verse": "25:20",
      "lineIndex": 131
    },
    {
      "start": 420.682,
      "end": 423.19,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I have spoken plainly that ye cannot err.",
      "verse": "25:20",
      "lineIndex": 132
    },
    {
      "start": 423.37,
      "end": 425.181,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And as the Lord God liveth",
      "verse": "25:20",
      "lineIndex": 133
    },
    {
      "start": 425.361,
      "end": 428.89,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that brought Israel up out of the land of Egypt,",
      "verse": "25:20",
      "lineIndex": 134
    },
    {
      "start": 429.07,
      "end": 432.46,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and gave unto Moses power that he should heal the nations",
      "verse": "25:20",
      "lineIndex": 135
    },
    {
      "start": 432.64,
      "end": 435.937,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "after they had been bitten by the poisonous serpents,",
      "verse": "25:20",
      "lineIndex": 136
    },
    {
      "start": 436.117,
      "end": 438.996,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "if they would cast their eyes unto the serpent",
      "verse": "25:20",
      "lineIndex": 137
    },
    {
      "start": 439.176,
      "end": 441.312,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which he did raise up before them,",
      "verse": "25:20",
      "lineIndex": 138
    },
    {
      "start": 441.492,
      "end": 444.836,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also gave him power that he should smite the rock",
      "verse": "25:20",
      "lineIndex": 139
    },
    {
      "start": 445.016,
      "end": 447.152,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the water should come forth;",
      "verse": "25:20",
      "lineIndex": 140
    },
    {
      "start": 447.332,
      "end": 449.097,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yea, behold I say unto you",
      "verse": "25:20",
      "lineIndex": 141
    },
    {
      "start": 449.277,
      "end": 451.181,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that as these things are true,",
      "verse": "25:20",
      "lineIndex": 142
    },
    {
      "start": 451.361,
      "end": 453.265,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and as the Lord God liveth,",
      "verse": "25:20",
      "lineIndex": 143
    },
    {
      "start": 453.445,
      "end": 456.928,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "there is none other name given under heaven",
      "verse": "25:20",
      "lineIndex": 144
    },
    {
      "start": 457.108,
      "end": 459.244,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "save it be this Jesus Christ,",
      "verse": "25:20",
      "lineIndex": 145
    },
    {
      "start": 459.424,
      "end": 461.421,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "of which I have spoken,",
      "verse": "25:20",
      "lineIndex": 146
    },
    {
      "start": 461.601,
      "end": 463.366,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "whereby man can be saved.",
      "verse": "25:20",
      "lineIndex": 147
    },
    {
      "start": 464.046,
      "end": 467.668,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore, for this cause hath the Lord God promised unto me",
      "verse": "25:21",
      "lineIndex": 148
    },
    {
      "start": 467.848,
      "end": 471.749,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that these things which I write shall be kept and preserved,",
      "verse": "25:21",
      "lineIndex": 149
    },
    {
      "start": 471.929,
      "end": 473.926,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and handed down unto my seed,",
      "verse": "25:21",
      "lineIndex": 150
    },
    {
      "start": 474.106,
      "end": 476.242,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "from generation to generation,",
      "verse": "25:21",
      "lineIndex": 151
    },
    {
      "start": 476.422,
      "end": 479.533,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that the promise may be fulfilled unto Joseph,",
      "verse": "25:21",
      "lineIndex": 152
    },
    {
      "start": 479.713,
      "end": 483.382,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that his seed should never perish as long as the earth should stand.",
      "verse": "25:21",
      "lineIndex": 153
    },
    {
      "start": 484.062,
      "end": 489.31,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore, these things shall go from generation to generation",
      "verse": "25:22",
      "lineIndex": 154
    },
    {
      "start": 489.49,
      "end": 491.766,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "as long as the earth shall stand;",
      "verse": "25:22",
      "lineIndex": 155
    },
    {
      "start": 491.946,
      "end": 495.893,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they shall go according to the will and pleasure of God;",
      "verse": "25:22",
      "lineIndex": 156
    },
    {
      "start": 496.073,
      "end": 500.067,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the nations who shall possess them shall be judged of them",
      "verse": "25:22",
      "lineIndex": 157
    },
    {
      "start": 500.247,
      "end": 502.29,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "according to the words which are written.",
      "verse": "25:22",
      "lineIndex": 158
    },
    {
      "start": 502.97,
      "end": 505.338,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "For we labor diligently to write,",
      "verse": "25:23",
      "lineIndex": 159
    },
    {
      "start": 505.518,
      "end": 507.097,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "to persuade our children,",
      "verse": "25:23",
      "lineIndex": 160
    },
    {
      "start": 507.277,
      "end": 509.088,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also our brethren,",
      "verse": "25:23",
      "lineIndex": 161
    },
    {
      "start": 509.268,
      "end": 510.94,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "to believe in Christ,",
      "verse": "25:23",
      "lineIndex": 162
    },
    {
      "start": 511.12,
      "end": 512.978,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and to be reconciled to God;",
      "verse": "25:23",
      "lineIndex": 163
    },
    {
      "start": 513.158,
      "end": 516.827,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for we know that it is by grace that we are saved,",
      "verse": "25:23",
      "lineIndex": 164
    },
    {
      "start": 517.007,
      "end": 518.772,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "after all we can do.",
      "verse": "25:23",
      "lineIndex": 165
    },
    {
      "start": 519.452,
      "end": 522.192,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And, notwithstanding we believe in Christ,",
      "verse": "25:24",
      "lineIndex": 166
    },
    {
      "start": 522.372,
      "end": 524.137,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "we keep the law of Moses,",
      "verse": "25:24",
      "lineIndex": 167
    },
    {
      "start": 524.317,
      "end": 527.336,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and look forward with steadfastness unto Christ,",
      "verse": "25:24",
      "lineIndex": 168
    },
    {
      "start": 527.516,
      "end": 529.792,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "until the law shall be fulfilled.",
      "verse": "25:24",
      "lineIndex": 169
    },
    {
      "start": 530.472,
      "end": 532.933,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "For, for this end was the law given;",
      "verse": "25:25",
      "lineIndex": 170
    },
    {
      "start": 533.113,
      "end": 536.224,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherefore the law hath become dead unto us,",
      "verse": "25:25",
      "lineIndex": 171
    },
    {
      "start": 536.404,
      "end": 539.515,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and we are made alive in Christ because of our faith;",
      "verse": "25:25",
      "lineIndex": 172
    },
    {
      "start": 539.695,
      "end": 542.296,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yet we keep the law because of the commandments.",
      "verse": "25:25",
      "lineIndex": 173
    },
    {
      "start": 542.976,
      "end": 544.462,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And we talk of Christ,",
      "verse": "25:26",
      "lineIndex": 174
    },
    {
      "start": 544.642,
      "end": 546.314,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "we rejoice in Christ,",
      "verse": "25:26",
      "lineIndex": 175
    },
    {
      "start": 546.494,
      "end": 547.98,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "we preach of Christ,",
      "verse": "25:26",
      "lineIndex": 176
    },
    {
      "start": 548.16,
      "end": 549.785,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "we prophesy of Christ,",
      "verse": "25:26",
      "lineIndex": 177
    },
    {
      "start": 549.965,
      "end": 552.38,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and we write according to our prophecies,",
      "verse": "25:26",
      "lineIndex": 178
    },
    {
      "start": 552.56,
      "end": 556.182,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that our children may know to what source they may look",
      "verse": "25:26",
      "lineIndex": 179
    },
    {
      "start": 556.362,
      "end": 558.452,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for a remission of their sins.",
      "verse": "25:26",
      "lineIndex": 180
    },
    {
      "start": 559.132,
      "end": 561.222,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore, we speak concerning the law",
      "verse": "25:27",
      "lineIndex": 181
    },
    {
      "start": 561.402,
      "end": 564.374,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that our children may know the deadness of the law;",
      "verse": "25:27",
      "lineIndex": 182
    },
    {
      "start": 564.554,
      "end": 565.576,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they,",
      "verse": "25:27",
      "lineIndex": 183
    },
    {
      "start": 565.756,
      "end": 567.985,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "by knowing the deadness of the law,",
      "verse": "25:27",
      "lineIndex": 184
    },
    {
      "start": 568.165,
      "end": 571.23,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "may look forward unto that life which is in Christ,",
      "verse": "25:27",
      "lineIndex": 185
    },
    {
      "start": 571.41,
      "end": 574.104,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and know for what end the law was given.",
      "verse": "25:27",
      "lineIndex": 186
    },
    {
      "start": 574.284,
      "end": 576.885,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And after the law is fulfilled in Christ,",
      "verse": "25:27",
      "lineIndex": 187
    },
    {
      "start": 577.065,
      "end": 580.084,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that they need not harden their hearts against him",
      "verse": "25:27",
      "lineIndex": 188
    },
    {
      "start": 580.264,
      "end": 582.632,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "when the law ought to be done away.",
      "verse": "25:27",
      "lineIndex": 189
    },
    {
      "start": 583.312,
      "end": 586.47,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And now behold, my people, ye are a stiffnecked people;",
      "verse": "25:28",
      "lineIndex": 190
    },
    {
      "start": 586.65,
      "end": 589.39,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherefore, I have spoken plainly unto you,",
      "verse": "25:28",
      "lineIndex": 191
    },
    {
      "start": 589.57,
      "end": 591.335,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that ye cannot misunderstand.",
      "verse": "25:28",
      "lineIndex": 192
    },
    {
      "start": 591.515,
      "end": 596.252,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And the words which I have spoken shall stand as a testimony against you;",
      "verse": "25:28",
      "lineIndex": 193
    },
    {
      "start": 596.432,
      "end": 600.101,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for they are sufficient to teach any man the right way;",
      "verse": "25:28",
      "lineIndex": 194
    },
    {
      "start": 600.281,
      "end": 603.764,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for the right way is to believe in Christ and deny him not;",
      "verse": "25:28",
      "lineIndex": 195
    },
    {
      "start": 603.944,
      "end": 607.195,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for by denying him ye also deny the prophets and the law.",
      "verse": "25:28",
      "lineIndex": 196
    },
    {
      "start": 607.875,
      "end": 609.965,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And now behold, I say unto you",
      "verse": "25:29",
      "lineIndex": 197
    },
    {
      "start": 610.145,
      "end": 612.746,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that the right way is to believe in Christ,",
      "verse": "25:29",
      "lineIndex": 198
    },
    {
      "start": 612.926,
      "end": 614.319,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and deny him not;",
      "verse": "25:29",
      "lineIndex": 199
    },
    {
      "start": 614.499,
      "end": 616.914,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and Christ is the Holy One of Israel;",
      "verse": "25:29",
      "lineIndex": 200
    },
    {
      "start": 617.094,
      "end": 619.695,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherefore ye must bow down before him,",
      "verse": "25:29",
      "lineIndex": 201
    },
    {
      "start": 619.875,
      "end": 622.986,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and worship him with all your might, mind and strength,",
      "verse": "25:29",
      "lineIndex": 202
    },
    {
      "start": 623.166,
      "end": 624.606,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and your whole soul;",
      "verse": "25:29",
      "lineIndex": 203
    },
    {
      "start": 624.786,
      "end": 627.99,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and if ye do this ye shall in nowise be cast out.",
      "verse": "25:29",
      "lineIndex": 204
    },
    {
      "start": 628.67,
      "end": 631.456,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And, inasmuch as it shall be expedient,",
      "verse": "25:30",
      "lineIndex": 205
    },
    {
      "start": 631.636,
      "end": 634.933,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "ye must keep the performances and ordinances of God",
      "verse": "25:30",
      "lineIndex": 206
    },
    {
      "start": 635.113,
      "end": 638.596,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "until the law shall be fulfilled which was given unto Moses.",
      "verse": "25:30",
      "lineIndex": 207
    }
  ]
}